description: Removes one or more tags (keys and values) from an Amazon Security Lake resource: a subscriber, or the data lake configuration for your Amazon Web Services account in a particular Amazon Web Services Region.

parameters.name: resourceArn
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Amazon Security Lake resource to remove one or more tags from.

parameters.name: tagKeys
parameters.description: A list of one or more tag keys. For each value in the list, specify the tag key for a tag to remove from the Amazon Security Lake resource. (string) ---
